{"tid":496529,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無良賊跟蹤婆婆入屋 搜掠逾萬元金飾現金","createTime":"2017-12-11T18:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T18:29:27.000Z","uid":10958,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"13a245e45cecf73cdc49dd4f57d1761821310189","tid":496529,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T18:28:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><br />\n無良賊跟蹤婆婆入屋 搜掠逾萬元金飾現金 </strong><br />\n<br />\n【22:28】新增動新聞<br />\n【20:10】警方正追緝一名年約40歲，中等身材，約5呎7吋高，操本地話男子，案發時身穿黃色短袖上衣及戴黑色鴨舌帽。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/12/12/3502676/20171211_ccm_09NEWNEW_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F3502676%2F20171211_ccm_09NEWNEW_w.mp4&d=tuGvIcROGMhMWQwFqHGIOJzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=0f5a86ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/12/12/3502676/20171211_ccm_09NEWNEW_w.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n黃大仙下邨龍輝樓，下午1時許，80歲姓汪婆婆從外返家，一名男子原來一直尾隨跟蹤她，直至汪婆婆開門欲入屋之際，男賊突閃出推跌婆婆，並入屋大肆搜掠，劫去內藏1萬元現金的櫃桶，得手後即奪門而逃，汪婆婆落樓通知姓鄧保安員報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171211/large/1512981819_c6b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171211%2Flarge%2F1512981819_c6b5.jpg&h=d4d31b53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171211/large/1512981820_de32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171211%2Flarge%2F1512981820_de32.jpg&h=3bd34084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場，婆婆報稱沒有受傷，不需送院，案件由黃大仙警區刑事調查隊第二隊跟進。警方正追緝一名年約40歲，中等身材，約5呎7吋高，操本地話男子，案發時身穿黃色短袖上衣及戴黑色鴨舌帽。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171211/57567729\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171211%2F57567729&d=tuGvIcROGMhMWQwFqHGIOJzN29